    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 2 · RAG agent (with memory)\n**gpt-5.4-mini** agent (+ fallback) with **conversation memory** (Simple Memory keyed by `reportId`) searches **only this report's** pages (Vector Store filtered by `report_id`) and answers from them. Same embedding model as ingest.",
        "height": 1010,
        "width": 910,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "a4cf090b-2b9d-57de-9490-d7d1c1dba939",
